high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the kitchen island, then turn right and walk to the section of counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the potato off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the potato in the sink basin and turn the water on, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean potato.
Turn around and walk over to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave door and place the clean potato inside to the left of the egg, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.
